<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV16">
<l>palapala vūḻika ḷāyiṭu maṉṟiyōr nāḻikaiyaip</l>
<l>palapala kūṟiṭṭa kūṟāyi ṭuṅkaṇṇaṉ viṇṇaṉaiyāyp</l>
<l>palapala nāḷaṉpar kūṭilu nīṅkilum yāmelitum</l>
<l>palapala cūḻalu ṭaittamma vāḻiyip pāyiruḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You like the heaven of Kaṇṇaṉ who, besides bestowing [time] as many many aeons,</l>
<l>bestows one hour as the fraction that is set in many many fractions,</l>
<l>for many many days, whether [our] loved one meets or leaves [us], we will weaken.</l>
<l>Many many stratagems possesses it, alas, let it live, this spreading darkness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
